        <h2>Taking Back Control</h2>
        <p>The good news is you have choices. Apps that respect your privacy do exist. Look for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>One-time purchase models (aligned incentives)</li>
          <li>Offline-first functionality</li>
          <li>No account requirements</li>
          <li>Clear, readable privacy policies</li>
          <li>Open about their data practices</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Your health data is yours. It's time we treated it that way.</p>
